#

Caramel Apple Upside-Down Cake

$15
350 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

DairyEggs

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-Free

Tags:

DessertCakeFruitySeasonal

Description

A delightful twist on a classic dessert, featuring caramelized apples atop a moist vanilla cake, perfect for any occasion.

Ingredients

  • Granny Smith Apples: 3, peeled and sliced
  • Unsalted Butter: 1/2 cup
  • Brown Sugar: 3/4 cup
  • Granulated Sugar: 1/2 cup
  • All-Purpose Flour: 1 1/2 cups
  • Baking Powder: 2 teaspoons
  • Salt: 1/2 teaspoon
  • Vanilla Extract: 1 teaspoon
  • Large Eggs: 2
  • Milk: 1/2 cup
